data.description: Welcome To Your Next Home! Come See This Newer East Facing 2018 Build Situated On A Spacious Corner Lot In Quiet Neighborhood, Yet Just A Short Drive Into Bentonville Or Centerton. Full Brick Exterior. Inside Offers Wood Look Tile Throughout The Main Living Areas, Tile In Bathrooms/Laundry, Carpet In Bedrooms. Spacious Living Area w/ Brick Fireplace. Kitchen Offers Island/Bar Seating + Eat-in Dining, Tile Backsplash, Walk-in Pantry. Primary Suite w/ Split Dual Vanity, Soaker Tub, Tile Shower, Walk-in In Primary Bath. Split Floorplan. Covered Front Porch And Back Patio. Fenced Yard. RD ZERO DOWN ELIGIBLE. Immaculate Home, Come See! Seller to pay $10,000 towards buyers closing costs, prepaids, rate buy down and any other allowable expenses.
